{"tid":626643,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"【I/A】Brown Dust (17) - 1001開POST","createTime":"2018-04-12T09:43:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-12T10:45:58.000Z","uid":12100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bc65078df379d1380a808d7af6716d6e3cc25c4f","tid":626643,"uid":12100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T09:43:42.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">韓國 NEOWIZ 3月6日宣佈戰略指令RPG《Brown Dust》（iOS/Android）預定於3月7日正式配信。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/195505_47e0b0012668b40f6186d1601bdaf883.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F195505_47e0b0012668b40f6186d1601bdaf883.jpg&h=4930ba47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/195509_8788c08b0778aae6ff1a0aad46096130.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F195509_8788c08b0778aae6ff1a0aad46096130.jpg&h=e2c3f92e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/195512_e66449a702abdae8637047bf9e29d66b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F195512_e66449a702abdae8637047bf9e29d66b.jpg&h=8ea46a94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/195516_7da5ea65940162c195614437c60069d3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F195516_7da5ea65940162c195614437c60069d3.jpg&h=48b52cd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/195525_c9708864050718f395240c097b62ccbd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F195525_c9708864050718f395240c097b62ccbd.jpg&h=09636aa8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/195417_7a56d2bff3b5268a5d22dc56ff713f79.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F195417_7a56d2bff3b5268a5d22dc56ff713f79.jpg&h=40f0c136&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/195425_74d2e66348966c75afb1de4dc71a9798.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F195425_74d2e66348966c75afb1de4dc71a9798.jpg&h=74ffb367&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/195425_7e40d6e4c1be56043a2d89f554e7699a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F195425_7e40d6e4c1be56043a2d89f554e7699a.jpg&h=00fb64b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/195428_df6bffcb857dcc78bb622cb80dabe3df.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F195428_df6bffcb857dcc78bb622cb80dabe3df.jpg&h=658c68d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/195431_6d6535319addf94d38760631f2d7a5c0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F195431_6d6535319addf94d38760631f2d7a5c0.jpg&h=ae7b04f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/195432_06538f7ef197b7713ba460ec9266003b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F195432_06538f7ef197b7713ba460ec9266003b.jpg&h=226e900c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n目前遊戲的事前登錄人數已突破15萬人，是故已確定遊戲推出後，全部玩家將可獲得相等於一個十連轉蛋份量的600個鑽石以及「☆5傭兵確定券」。<br />\n<br />\n遊戲核心內容是陣營配置，先在戰前佈置我方十體傭兵角色，再在戰鬥階段時接雙方角色的攻勢移動順來互相攻擊。作品之內有多達300名角色，而且全都均可提升至最高階級別。<br />\n<br />\nIOS：<a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/jp/app/id1299021478\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fjp%2Fapp%2Fid1299021478&d=jWlCGUlyUx1sda%2BvdaxSjJWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=ca626533\" target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/jp/app/id1299021478</a><br />\nAN：<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.neowizgames.game.browndust.srpg.global\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.neowizgames.game.browndust.srpg.global&d=jWlCGUlyUx1sda%2BvdaxSjJWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=c8c8d119\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.neowizgames.game.browndust.srpg.global</a><br />\nQooApp：<a href=\"https://apps.qoo-app.com/app/6042\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.qoo-app.com%2Fapp%2F6042&d=jWlCGUlyUx1sda%2BvdaxSjJWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=12ff2bcc\" target=\"_blank\">https://apps.qoo-app.com/app/6042</a></div>"},{"pid":"ac40cd68a55699231a0ba2171cb9b8832417c1fc","tid":626643,"uid":12100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T09:43:57.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">【照顧絲打/基巴區】</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/195804_42f30c25e5fef448db62d7c6c9b6762b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F195804_42f30c25e5fef448db62d7c6c9b6762b.jpg&h=d16019f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/195807_b0341269fd21723090a3169103438a34.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F195807_b0341269fd21723090a3169103438a34.jpg&h=9bb96aa6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/195810_b5fab7dd8a30734ee53ea2a46db8b6be.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F195810_b5fab7dd8a30734ee53ea2a46db8b6be.jpg&h=85fe362e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/195812_821682b225905978953e0f97e65b0ab9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F195812_821682b225905978953e0f97e65b0ab9.jpg&h=2be19d6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/195814_abf34b3c931bee1138125c896371a5d9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F195814_abf34b3c931bee1138125c896371a5d9.jpg&h=772e1c82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/12/123528_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F12%2F123528_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=75182308&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">【攻略】</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">日版速刷首抽方法 (遊戲內建)<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=32104&amp;snA=4&amp;tnum=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D32104%26snA%3D4%26tnum%3D3&d=jWlCGUlyUx1sda%2BvdaxSjJWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=a2eedc7a\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=32104&amp;snA=4&amp;tnum=3</a><br />\n右上角設定<br />\nPLUG下方那排日文 點下去<br />\n打上Reset 就重來了</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【日本評價網】</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://wiki.denfaminicogamer.jp/browndust/%E3%83%AA%E3%82%BB%E3%83%9E%E3%83%A9%E3%83%A9%E3%83%B3%E3%82%AD%E3%83%B3%E3%82%B0?comment=3#comment\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwiki.denfaminicogamer.jp%2Fbrowndust%2F%25E3%2583%25AA%25E3%2582%25BB%25E3%2583%259E%25E3%2583%25A9%25E3%2583%25A9%25E3%2583%25B3%25E3%2582%25AD%25E3%2583%25B3%25E3%2582%25B0%3Fcomment%3D3%23comment&d=jWlCGUlyUx1sda%2BvdaxSjJWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=0dde02e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://wiki.denfaminicogamer.jp/browndust/%E3%83%AA%E3%82%BB%E3%83%9E%E3%83%A9%E3%83%A9%E3%83%B3%E3%82%AD%E3%83%B3%E3%82%B0?comment=3#comment</a></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【大陸仔評價】</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://img.ngacn.cc/attachments/mon_201803/07/bwQ5-8dk6ZiT1kShs-ob.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ngacn.cc%2Fattachments%2Fmon_201803%2F07%2FbwQ5-8dk6ZiT1kShs-ob.jpg&h=3ffd2e70&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://img.ngacn.cc/attachments/mon_201803/07/bwQ5-6cy1ZfT3cSoa-hs.jpg.medium.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ngacn.cc%2Fattachments%2Fmon_201803%2F07%2FbwQ5-6cy1ZfT3cSoa-hs.jpg.medium.jpg&h=5733e4be&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【升星方法】</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://c.kekeke.cc/t/FmVevFK97u.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc.kekeke.cc%2Ft%2FFmVevFK97u.jpeg&h=1498bddf&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n張圖死左, 大致上就係刷一般券抽狗糧(銀色星既角色), 升LV, 跟住昇級由1星升2星, 2星升3星, 漫漫長路升到5星再比5星角食<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【韓服圖鑑】</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://mega.nz/#!ZBAUWIKY!XxV3tpkf_YXJ10VkklJbGCDQOws4rhJi10APPqHmer8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmega.nz%2F%23%21ZBAUWIKY%21XxV3tpkf_YXJ10VkklJbGCDQOws4rhJi10APPqHmer8&d=jWlCGUlyUx1sda%2BvdaxSjJWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=8f3721bb\" target=\"_blank\">https://mega.nz/#!ZBAUWIKY!XxV3tpkf_YXJ10VkklJbGCDQOws4rhJi10APPqHmer8</a></div><br />\n\f"},{"pid":"a94025e0af138797a05512b26a1b4c4040ba78ac","tid":626643,"uid":12100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T09:44:08.000Z","msg":"Q&amp;A:<br />\n<br />\nQ:隻驚洗唔洗刷首抽<br />\nA:最好就刷 因為抽五星機率只係1% 十次十連都唔中係經常既事<br />\n<br />\nQ:刷到歌基+是但一隻開唔開波好<br />\nA:開 再問就ban<br />\n<br />\nQ:課咩野包係最抵屌<br />\nA:新手500%<br />\n<br />\nQ:隻驚好似好複雜 唔知點樣玩<br />\nA:呢隻驚好似捉棋咁 放錯人錯順序都會影響哂成場結果 自己慢慢摸索啦<br />\n<br />\nQ:好多體力唔知點洗好<br />\nA:新手一開始就衝主線 唔夠打就刷符紋/肥料升主力<br />\n<br />\nQ:無錢又無肥 幾時先有得刷肥關<br />\nA:星期五至日或日本假期特定時間 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZCbmg74XISk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DZCbmg74XISk&d=jWlCGUlyUx1sda%2BvdaxSjJWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=1b63b03b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZCbmg74XISk</a><br />\n打錢關最快放法<br />\n<br />\nQ:抽咩pool好<br />\nA:暫時係魅法同大叔坦既POOL2<br />\n<br />\nQ:抽到好多三星做唔做升星肥好<br />\nA:唔做 好多三星都有用 廢既就將佢+9 兩隻+9合一隻原四<br />\n<br />\nQ:抽到重覆五星食唔食好<br />\nA:隻野勁就食 廢就做升星肥<br />\n<br />\nQ:sup狀態會放邊 唔識用<br />\nA:下一個順序<br />\n<br />\nQ:隻驚肝唔肝<br />\nA:唔肝、因為可以掛機打素材，但係唔會失樂趣 因為掛機成日會唔夠打 而且pvp 公會戰 地下城 搶礦 打符文高層 全部都係要用腦去諗同試 <br />\n<br />\nQ:無課玩唔玩到<br />\nA:玩到 育成Game課左只會資源黎得較快 <br />\n<br />\nQ:六魔星點有<br />\nA:無得首抽 用魔幣換<br />\n<br />\nQ:點樣買體係最抵<br />\nA:神秘島係有粉既情況 係交易所用石刷商店買體 抵過直接用石買<br />\n<br />\nQ:敏捷有咩用<br />\nA:被攻擊時有機率觸發減35%傷 debuff持續時間減半<br />\n<br />\nQ:可唔可以一次過升星 逐隻逐隻禁好煩<br />\nA:可以 去升星畫面左下個傭兵選擇 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/18/124319_df4328360824ac5145095d454cd2a143.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F18%2F124319_df4328360824ac5145095d454cd2a143.png&h=514166a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ: 邊隻先解到歌雞招魅惑？<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/22/091402_3a0de14d008f7c694837eca11f394deb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F22%2F091402_3a0de14d008f7c694837eca11f394deb.png&h=ac04bad0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nA: 隻驚分免疫同淨化，免疫只可以防止中，已經中咗既話無用<br />\n淨化只可以解，未中既話無用<br />\n免疫：<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/22/091518_0ff0a3d73e6d6aa1d6deddaa9fdde263.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F22%2F091518_0ff0a3d73e6d6aa1d6deddaa9fdde263.png&h=9e2ad084&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/22/091527_64befa18637bf0cb5338cecd2e1b0d5c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F22%2F091527_64befa18637bf0cb5338cecd2e1b0d5c.png&h=2eb9f16a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n淨化：<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/22/091538_abf557f17822f530a5457e4ab1cadc95.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F22%2F091538_abf557f17822f530a5457e4ab1cadc95.png&h=020f904c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ:<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/22/091916_c7da2202001ef3739c67954b4c9dbb31.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F22%2F091916_c7da2202001ef3739c67954b4c9dbb31.PNG&h=768cb619&s={SIZE}\" />呢兩個咩黎?<br />\nA:上面係暴擊率，下面係暴擊時既額外傷害[/quote]<br />\n<br />\nQ:SET左掛機之後去訓覺, 唔通又要較埋鬧鐘起身閂機?<br />\nA:<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Tcleg0r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FTcleg0r.jpg&h=e83d4f5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ:綠盾要點先有?<br />\nA:去傭兵合成果度合, 用4隻4星合出黎, 其中阿叔果隻4星係用4隻3星合, 當中最難有果隻臭雞(アセラ)要用P點抽<br />\n<br />\nQ:任務個30日FEST我有日唔小心做唔完, 係咪收得皮?<br />\nA:30日既意思係你30日內每日做晒就最快30日拎到, 做慢左咪遲D拎到, 做完會繼續有第2個30日重新開始\f"},{"pid":"5a43730ed238d694d0bb6c5bb1b4da52e8323a24","tid":626643,"uid":12100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T09:44:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>lihkg 1<br />\nlihkg 2<br />\nlihkg 4<br />\nlihkg 7<br />\nlihkg 8<br />\nlihkg 9<br />\nlihkg10<br />\n澳門首家線上賭場啦<br />\nHKG香港<br />\n<br />\n以上為真 連登公會 （隨時再update） <br />\n新玩巴打注意, 唔係list入面唔關連登事</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"6efa11b20b0af015065a69afc5cae0fe78d2ce50","tid":626643,"uid":12100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T09:45:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">惡魔城攻略</span><br />\n1-5關高防關<br />\n6-10關炸彈關<br />\n11-15關肥仔關<br />\n16-20關控場關<br />\n等巴打SHARE<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">ルーンの寺院攻略</span><br />\n等巴打SHARE"},{"pid":"38c366ffc9e7fd1a5b59ddd455d342a1563bdbed","tid":626643,"uid":12100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T09:46:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/623566/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/623566/page/1</a><br />\nPost 16 Link"},{"pid":"4af6026098953faea55107f5e1ca5a53a5d630f2","tid":626643,"uid":52234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T09:46:41.000Z","msg":"開得太急 唔記得改17<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31b602ff2c9ce2972c10c3a0e2c969f0c2581d21","tid":626643,"uid":12514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T09:47:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/12/174711_35ab825a6de2bd6fe7f6ac637a6179ba.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F12%2F174711_35ab825a6de2bd6fe7f6ac637a6179ba.jpeg&h=a145f89a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大陸仔最新評價"},{"pid":"ead41f2251757fe673246a381899e110223502b4","tid":626643,"uid":12100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4af6026098953faea55107f5e1ca5a53a5d630f2","tid":626643,"uid":52234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T09:46:41.000Z","msg":"開得太急 唔記得改17<img src=\"/assets/f